---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import release from '../data/release.json';
---
<BaseLayout
    title="FBIde changelog"
    description="Release notes for FBIde."
    activeNav="changelog"
>
    <section>
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="h2">Changelog</h1>
            <p class="text-muted">
                Release notes for the latest FBIde build. The full release log lives on the
                <a href={`${release.githubRepo}/releases`}>GitHub releases page</a>.
            </p>

            <article>
                <h2 class="h4">FBIde {release.version}</h2>
                <p class="date">{release.releaseDate}</p>
                <p>
                    First public pre-release of the FBIde rewrite. The codebase is now a clean
                    modern C++23 project built on wxWidgets 3.3, with the original FBIde feature
                    set restored on top.
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Editor: syntax highlighting, code folding, auto-indent, context-sensitive help.</li>
                    <li>Compiler integration: compile, run, quick-run, parameters dialog, command prompt.</li>
                    <li>Tooling: code formatter (case conversion + reformat), Sub / Function browser,
                        multi-line find / replace, recent files, multi-document tabs.</li>
                    <li>Themes: Borland, Classic, Matrix, Modern (light + dark), Obsidian, Ocean, Twilight.</li>
                    <li>Localisation: English plus a dozen language translations.</li>
                    <li>Single-instance handling, drag-and-drop file open, command-line arguments.</li>
                </ul>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
